data.description: Beautiful 6 bedroom 3 1/2 bath home on a private lake. What more could you ask for? This home boast 2 kitchens and 2 laundry areas close to the bedrooms so no more carrying laundry around the house. Separate formal dining and living room. Open concept kitchen/family room with great views of the lake. Loads of potential and perfect for a large or multi-generational family. Fantastic covered outdoor space on main level and screened porch on basement level. AWESOME view of the lake! Nice quiet neighborhood minutes from Hiram and Douglasville.
